## Pending live commands

Mac receiver command, to be run by the Mac orchestrator after syncing this branch:

```sh
cargo run -q -p madobectl -- \
  video-smoke receive \
  --bind 0.0.0.0:47044 \
  --evidence-dir evidence/m3-cross-device-video-smoke/macos
```

Linux sender command, to be run after Mac posts its reachable receiver address:

```sh
cargo run -q -p madobectl -- \
  video-smoke send \
  --addr <mac-receiver-ip>:47044 \
  --sample evidence/m2-nvenc-encode-sample/sample-av1.ivf \
  --evidence-dir evidence/m3-cross-device-video-smoke/linux
```
